name: json-c
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.12" %}

package:
    name: json-c
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: json-c-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://s3.amazonaws.com/json-c_releases/releases/json-c-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    md5: 3ca4bbb881dfc4017e8021b5e0a8c491

build:
    number: 0
    skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
    build:
        - autoconf
        - automake
        - libtool

test:
    commands:
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/lib/libjson-c.a  # [unix]
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/lib/libjson-c.so  # [linux]
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/lib/libjson-c.dylib  # [osx]
        - conda inspect linkages -n _test json-c  # [linux]

about:
    home: https://github.com/json-c/json-c/wiki
    license: MIT
    summary: A JSON implementation in C

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
